.TH "_add_link" 9 "_add_link" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
_add_link \- add an interconnect between two IP blocks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" _add_link
.BI "(struct omap_hwmod_ocp_if *oi "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "oi" 12
pointer to a struct omap_hwmod_ocp_if record
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Add struct omap_hwmod_link records connecting the slave IP block
specified in \fIoi->slave\fP to \fIoi\fP.  This code is assumed to run before
preemption or SMP has been enabled, thus avoiding the need for
locking in this code.  Changes to this assumption will require
additional locking.  Returns 0.
